---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import GalleryLightbox from '../../components/GalleryLightbox.astro';

const title = "Conture — Brand Identity for a Modern Beauty Salon | Aenea";
const description = "Conture is a brand identity by Aenea for a modern beauty salon — modern elegance through restraint, with clean lines, balanced proportions, and an earthy, grounded palette.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <Navbar current="work" />

  <main>
    <section class="proj-intro wrap">
      <a href="/work" class="back-link"><span aria-hidden="true">←</span> Selected Work</a>
      <span class="eyebrow proj-cat">Brand Identity</span>
      <h1 class="proj-title">Conture</h1>
      <p class="proj-lead">A brand identity for a modern beauty salon — modern elegance expressed through what&rsquo;s left out, where minimalism is a structural decision that lets detail and tone speak without competition.</p>
      <div class="proj-meta">
        <div><div class="meta-k">Service</div><div class="meta-v">Brand Identity</div></div>
        <div><div class="meta-k">Sector</div><div class="meta-v">Beauty &amp; Wellness</div></div>
        <div><div class="meta-k">Year</div><div class="meta-v">2025</div></div>
        <div><div class="meta-k">Deliverables</div><div class="meta-v">Logotype, Identity system, Applications</div></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <figure class="bleed" data-lightbox>
      <img src="/conture-hero.jpg" alt="Conture brand identity — visual identity for a modern beauty salon, by Aenea" />
    </figure>

    <section class="case wrap">
      <div class="case-label"><span class="idx">01</span><span class="eyebrow">Overview</span></div>
      <div class="case-body">
        <p>The brand design for Conture Salon begins with a single idea: modern elegance expressed through what&rsquo;s left out. Restraint becomes the strategy — a quiet, confident foundation for a contemporary beauty brand.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="wrap">
      <div class="pair">
        <figure class="ph s7 r43" data-lightbox><img src="/conture-1.jpg" alt="Conture logotype — modern beauty salon identity by Aenea" /></figure>
        <figure class="ph s5 r45" data-lightbox><img src="/conture-2.jpg" alt="Conture brand system and spacing detail" /></figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case wrap">
      <div class="case-label"><span class="idx">02</span><span class="eyebrow">The Identity</span></div>
      <div class="case-body">
        <p>Clean lines and balanced proportions form the foundation. Minimalism here isn&rsquo;t a style choice — it&rsquo;s a structural decision that lets detail and tone speak without competition. Subtle contrasts and deliberate spacing give the identity its edge.</p>
        <p>The earthy palette grounds the brand in warmth. Muted neutrals and natural tones keep the design from feeling cold, creating an atmosphere that is sophisticated without distance.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="wrap">
      <div class="pair">
        <figure class="ph s5 r45" data-lightbox><img src="/conture-3.jpg" alt="Conture palette and brand application" /></figure>
        <figure class="ph s7 r43" data-lightbox><img src="/conture-4.jpg" alt="Conture identity across salon touchpoints" /></figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case wrap">
      <div class="case-label"><span class="idx">03</span><span class="eyebrow">Outcome</span></div>
      <div class="case-body">
        <p>The result is a brand that doesn&rsquo;t need to announce itself. It simply belongs — cohesive across every touchpoint, quietly confident in every application.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="next wrap">
      <a href="/work/eclat" class="next-link">
        <span class="next-k">Next project</span>
        <span class="next-title">Éclat <span class="arr" aria-hidden="true">↗</span></span>
        <span class="next-cat">Web Design</span>
      </a>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
  <GalleryLightbox />
</Layout>